# Correctness properties (must not be broken)

Non-negotiable behavioural invariants. Any change that violates one is incorrect and must be revised before merge.

| ID | Property |
|----|-----------|
| P1 | Patient Registration Creates Health Record — exactly one HealthRecord per new patient |
| P2 | Profile Update Round Trip — updated fields unchanged on subsequent read |
| P3 | Duplicate Registration Rejection — same phone/email → 409 `IDENTITY_CONFLICT` |
| P4 | Doctor Registration Starts Pending — new doctor status = pending immediately |
| P5 | License Verification State Transition — verified → active + notification; invalid → rejected + reason |
| P6 | Doctor Search Proximity Ordering — ascending distance when location sort enabled |
| P7 | Slot Hold Exclusivity — concurrent booking on held slot rejected within 10 minutes (Redis SET NX TTL) |
| P8 | Appointment Confirmation Notifies Both Parties |
| P9 | Early Cancellation Releases Slot — cancelled > 2h before → slot available + refund event |
| P10 | Recording Requires Consent — `recording_enabled` iff `recording_consent`; never without consent |
| P11 | Prescription Guard for Orders — valid active prescription; dispensed after use; second order rejected |
| P12 | Prescription Default Expiry — no explicit expiry → `expires_at = issued_at + 30 days` |
| P13 | Pharmacy Stock Filter — only pharmacies with qty > 0 for requested medication |
| P14 | Credit Score Determinism — same input → same score always (pure function) |
| P15 | Credit Balance Warning — balance > 80% of limit → warning notification |
| P16 | Payment Receipt Round Trip — completed payment → receipt referencing payment ID |
| P17 | Failed Payment Preserves Pending — failure → stays pending + failure notification |
| P18 | Medication Schedule Generation — dispensed → schedule with correct dose times |
| P19 | Missed Dose Detection — unconfirmed 2h after scheduled → `AdherenceEvent.status = missed` |
| P20 | Consecutive Missed Doses Alert — 3+ consecutive missed → notify ALL next-of-kin |
| P21 | Drug Interaction Alert Before Finalization — overlap → alert doctor before `active` |
| P22 | Emergency Alert Reaches All Next of Kin — no contacts omitted |
| P23 | Next of Kin Notification Retry — failed → at most 3 retries; failed after 3 |
| P24 | Health Record Access Control — read iff grant exists; denial → AuditLog |
| P25 | Low Stock Alert — qty ≤ `low_stock_threshold` → alert to pharmacy |
| P26 | Emergency Keyword Detection — crisis keyword → emergency options or Crisis Protocol |
| P27 | Prohibited Content Flagging — prohibited term → `flagged`; excluded from published list |
| P28 | One Rating Per Appointment — second rating rejected; original unchanged |
| P29 | Notification Log Completeness — every sent notification → `NotificationLog` |
| P30 | Critical Notification SMS Fallback — push fails for emergency/medication → SMS attempt |
| P31 | Account Lockout After Failed Logins — 5 failures → 423 `ACCOUNT_LOCKED` + notification |
| P32 | Lab Order Attached to Health Record — doctor-created order attached and queryable |
| P33 | Critical Lab Result Alert — `is_critical` → immediate alert to ordering doctor on upload |
| P34 | Consecutive Low Mood Prompt — last 3 mood logs rating 1 → mental health resource prompt |
| P35 | Child Growth Out-of-Range Alert — outside expected range → alert guardian |
| P36 | Referral Timeout Reminder — pending > 48h no response → reminder to receiving doctor |
| P37 | Second Opinion Access Restrictions — no prescriptions, record changes, or primary-only actions |
| P38 | Second Opinion Access Revocation — completed/declined → access revoked + logged |
| P39 | Referral Requires Patient Consent — shared sections need `patient_consent_at` before dispatch |
| P40 | Queue Position and Wait Time — join → `queue_position > 0` AND `estimated_wait_minutes >= 0` |
| P41 | Queue Recalculation on Delay — doctor delayed > 15min → recalculate waits + notify patients |
